ssets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ca993c422c7dad6b21c4a981da08d7edc059bf","tid":360847,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"我反而係老母年紀越大越自我中心<br />\n老豆後生個陣真係好自我好任性<br />\n成日乜都諗自己先<br />\n依家反而顧家左好多<br />\n好多事都開始會諗可能自己以前唔諗人感受先會咁<br />\n反觀我老母完全唔同<br />\n覺得好似佢自己做左好多然後全世界最慘係佢<br />\n最無辜又係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3592e5a37d63e582cf6ad37c3d7c58094cb133a1","tid":360847,"uid":131784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"根本系我老豆黎"},{"pid":"eeff954c7ae6cce9061d7d650a2d16f421daf062","tid":360847,"uid":93436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本系我老豆黎</blockquote><br />\n系你老母"}]}